Package: liblandlockconfig0
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Sandboxer library leveraging Landlock - shared library
 Landlockconfig provides a C shared library for sandboxing processes
 using Landlock with JSON or TOML configuration files.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: liblandlockconfig-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: liblandlockconfig0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Sandboxer library leveraging Landlock - development files
 Landlockconfig provides a C shared library for sandboxing processes
 using Landlock with JSON or TOML configuration files.
 .
 This package contains the C header, pkg-config file, and development
 symlink for building against liblandlockconfig.

Package: llconfig
Architecture: any
Section: utils
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Command-line sandboxer using Landlock with JSON/TOML configuration
 llconfig is a command-line tool that applies Landlock sandbox restrictions
 defined in JSON or TOML configuration files, then executes a given command
 within the sandbox.
 .
 It composes multiple configuration files and supports reading from files,
 directories, or standard input.
